OL,3,CWest Cumberland Hospital set to reopen
OL,4,Cafter #130 million investment
OL,6,FITV Border's Kieran MacFadzean went
OL,7,Falong to look at the new facility
OL,9,FWhitehaven's revamped West Cumberland
OL,10,FHospital is set to reopen to patients
OL,11,Flater this month.
OL,13,FThe multi-million pound development
OL,14,Fhas seen 40 per cent of the old
OL,15,Fhospital replaced with new, state-of-
OL,16,Fthe-art facilities including stroke
OL,17,Frehabilitation and palliative care.
