OL,3,CWest Cumberland Hospital set to reopen
OL,4,Cafter #130 million investment
OL,6,FThe hospital was the first built in
OL,7,FEngland following the creation of the
OL,8,FNHS, but a lot of it has not been
OL,9,Fupdated since it was opened by the
OL,10,FQueen Mother in the 1960s.
OL,12,FThe first phase of redevelopment,
OL,13,Fwhich saw #90 million pounds of
OL,14,Finvestment, was completed in 2015.
OL,16,FWork on phase two has been underway
OL,17,Fsince 2022 and has seen #40 million
OL,18,Finvested in updating old equipment
OL,19,Fwhich was deemed no longer fit for
OL,20,Fpurpose.
