OL,3,CWest Cumberland Hospital set to reopen
OL,4,Cafter #130 million investment
OL,6,FNew specialised features include a
OL,7,Frehab kitchen for stroke patients, a
OL,8,F"challenge path" to simulate outdoor
OL,9,Fterrains and an automated medication
OL,10,Fdispensing system.
OL,12,FThe redevelopment includes works on
OL,13,Ffour wards including a new children
OL,14,Fand young people's ward a stroke and
OL,15,Frehabilitation ward.
